properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Stranger, I am Ragnok Hornbreaker, once a proud guardian of labyrinths, now a seeker of justice within these cursed lands. Ironforge ahead is no longer a place of honorable toil but a labyrinth of greed, twisted by dwarves lost to envy and avarice. My brethren and I once respected their kind, but now, I ask you to challenge 15 of these corrupted souls. But be careful! These treachery dwarfs will stab you to death if you're not prepared! I advice you to go to Ilya's training room or sewers, to get some experience with harmless foes.
